 Bug Type:         PHP-GTK related
 Operating System: WinXP
 PHP Version:      5.2.12
 New Comment:

GtkFileSelection has been deprecated since Gtk 2.12, so the 2.0.1
release of PHP-GTK does not yet mark it deprecated.

However the example code for me is working perfectly.

Run your script and then in the selection box hit the tab key

Notice how only files/folders that match *.txt are now shown?

You can probably simulate the keypress in your code to make the filter
action transparent to the user.





